data.description: Assumable LOW interest rate VA loan!!!! Come make this 3bed/2ba with over 1800sqft in desirable SE neighborhood your home!!!! Home offers beautifully upgraded interior with pristine flooring, giving a modern and stylish feel throughout. Split floor plan, extra wide hallways, nice size primary bedroom with in suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The spacious rooms provide ample space for relaxation. Outside a finished back yard offers a perfect setting for gatherings, entertaining or simply enjoy a private outdoor oasis. To top it all off home includes PAID SOLAR!!!! Don't miss out schedule your private showing today!
